  "description": "A reddish-brown hawk is perched on a moss-covered branch of a tree, seen from a low angle. The hawk is facing slightly to the right, and its feathers are detailed and patterned with darker markings. The branch it's sitting on is textured with green moss and small buds. The background is a soft blur of green foliage and a bright, overcast sky, creating a natural and slightly muted aesthetic. Light filters through the leaves, creating dappled highlights.",
